!!! 5
html
  head
    meta(http-equiv='content-type', content='text/html; charset=utf-8')
    link(rel="stylesheet/less", type="text/css", href="css/welcome.less")
    script(src="js/less.min.js", type="text/javascript")
    title Slim driven by jade.php
  body
    h1 Welcome to Slim-Jade

    h2 What? 
    p This is a boilerplate. It's the
      a(href="http://www.slimframework.com/") Slim Framework 
      | with
      a(href="https://github.com/everzet/jade.php") jade.php
      | to render views

    h2 Why?
    p I like the Sinatra style MVC and love 
      a(href="http://jade-lang.com/") Jade. 
    p I prefer to use Node and Express, but needed to bang out something 
      | quick and I'm more proficient in PHP. So, Slim-Jade was born.

    h2 How?

    ol
      li git clone git@github.com:w33ble/slim-jade.git
      li cd slim-jade/vendor
      li git clone https://github.com/everzet/jade.php.git
      li git clone https://github.com/codeguy/Slim.git

    p Files of import:
    ul
        each item in files 
            li #{item}
